com.versant.common.dataservice
Class VDSMessage

java.lang.Object
  com.versant.common.dataservice.VDSMessage

public class VDSMessage
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a message object consisting of packed VDSObject and VDSClass objects. The content type of the message is indicated by its signature. Depending on a message's signature an appropriate object factory will be used to unpack it.
